┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     SCHOOL MANAGEMENT SYSTEM                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

1. ADMIN SETUP
   ├── Create Classes (Grade 10-A, Grade 10-B, etc.)
   ├── Create Teachers & Assign Subjects
   └── Set Academic Year

2. STUDENT REGISTRATION FLOW
   ├── Step 1: Create User Account (role: STUDENT)
   │   └── POST /api/v1/users/register
   │
   ├── Step 2: Create Student Profile
   │   ├── Link to User (userId)
   │   ├── Assign Class (classId)
   │   └── POST /api/v1/students
   │
   ├── Step 3: Create/Update Parent
   │   ├── Create Parent User Account (role: PARENT)
   │   ├── Create Parent Profile
   │   ├── Link Student to Parent (studentEmails)
   │   └── POST /api/v1/parents
   │
   └── Step 4: Assign Teacher (Already assigned via Class)

3. AFTER REGISTRATION - DATA RELATIONSHIPS
   ├── Student ←→ Class (Many-to-One)
   ├── Student ←→ Parent (Many-to-Many)
   ├── Class ←→ Teacher (Many-to-Many)
   └── Teacher ←→ Subjects (One-to-Many)

4. FRONTEND VIEWS
   ├── Student Dashboard
   │   ├── View Profile
   │   ├── View Class & Timetable
   │   ├── View Teachers
   │   └── View Parent Info
   │
   ├── Parent Dashboard
   │   ├── View Children's Profiles
   │   ├── Track Attendance
   │   └── View Grades
   │
   ├── Teacher Dashboard
   │   ├── View Assigned Classes
   │   ├── Mark Attendance
   │   └── Enter Grades
   │
   └── Admin Dashboard
       ├── Manage All Users
       ├── Create Classes
       ├── Assign Teachers
       └── Generate Reports